{"tid":1611800,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"破欠基金 問題","createTime":"2019-10-02T05:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T04:26:33.000Z","uid":95534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b59a61eb3e5b1c3e7af7b7bcbb98f604abbbfcba","tid":1611800,"uid":95534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:02:51.000Z","msg":"Sorry 想問下 應該向邊個部門投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事件：<br />\n（破欠7月頭 收到我地個case file, 而理論上 破欠係承諾左十星期內發放。 ）<br />\n<br />\n但另一樣令我要去投訴既原因係 <br />\n<br />\n9月頭破欠主任控電話比 僱主同我地（僱員）問一問details。 <br />\n之後僱主話我地（僱員）同同佢夾埋，叫僱主認左d薪金，待通知金等，去申請破欠。但僱主由頭到尾都沒有提交任何證據 口供, 只是同破欠部門講電話時提出一些沒有證實或可信性的口供。 <br />\n破欠就因為呢樣口講無憑的對話, 影響我地申請人: <br />\n1. 審核的程序及時間(差不多要延誤1個月或以上，你們破欠亦沒有一個準確的審核時間）<br />\n2. 我們申索人要專登請假 來比口供 <br />\n<br />\n我地（僱員）比完口供之後， 僱主又沒冇出席去比口供同證據。 現在破欠就好似拖我地時間，一直話審核我地既證據"},{"pid":"90c40c9e4a12ebcd34866e79fb03c6b401899483","tid":1611800,"uid":95534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558cdb60f0bf805bf74ce1352d1170c20146ac19","tid":1611800,"uid":95534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd0a0faf75fe33346850a21aaeaf697ee1688a9","tid":1611800,"uid":95534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145950ad92a9af7be9e93cb83719dd4b575ed6aa","tid":1611800,"uid":95534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda369b77ef46c85da6bd145cd0622a9f7a937fe","tid":1611800,"uid":95534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16